```plantuml
@startuml

' Class Diagram
class User {
    -email: String
    -password: String
    +login()
    +register()
}

class Interview {
    -questions: List<String>
    +startSession()
    +evaluateResponse()
}

class SpeechRecognition {
    +transcribeAudio()
}

class NonVerbalAnalysis {
    +evaluatePosture()
    +evaluateEyeContact()
}

class Feedback {
    +generateReport()
}

User --> Interview
Interview --> SpeechRecognition
Interview --> NonVerbalAnalysis
SpeechRecognition --> Feedback
NonVerbalAnalysis --> Feedback

@enduml
```

```plantuml
@startuml

' Sequence Diagram
actor User
participant "Oratis System" as System
participant "Speech Recognition" as SR
participant "Non-Verbal Analysis" as NVA
participant "Feedback Module" as FM

User -> System: Start Interview
System -> SR: Capture & Transcribe Speech
System -> NVA: Analyze Posture & Eye Contact
SR -> FM: Send Transcription Data
NVA -> FM: Send Non-Verbal Analysis
FM -> User: Provide Feedback

@enduml
```

